{"tid":1366060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"727 正名「一個人的遊行」!","createTime":"2019-07-26T00:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:31:06.000Z","uid":154585,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2085f9f76a385788e5d630f741a3e686918c7c33","tid":1366060,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"「一個人」的遊行，代表政府打壓人民集會權利，警方屈服於惡勢力威脅，引致只有「一個人」的集會遊行。<br />\n「一個人」的遊行，代表這是一個屬於有良知、有基本善惡觀念的「人」的一個遊行。<br />\n重申，「一個人的遊行」，遊行人士只有鐘健平一個人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相信今次遊行將會是歴史上最少人參與的一次遊行。請大家一同去見證歴史。</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc5443076c73fb1f6e80c4d6c1f1bd1fc9caac66","tid":1366060,"uid":281176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"774e2d4edc986474dc4c887549b3ff64b39f1071","tid":1366060,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5873f816a00efe261eb149548321adfd805b8f","tid":1366060,"uid":289262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"極權常用管治手段就係散播恐懼<br />\n怯你就輸成世<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ca1f7fdde56b3ddffc1712ce4533e8685547d463","tid":1366060,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"882955a3b2e47413464df13fe6a53481c1aabb54","tid":1366060,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayo0LYi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fayo0LYi.png&h=e3efb703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eca317dc142efd051975528f89f870c0732eeaf","tid":1366060,"uid":154585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"其實好擔心<br />\n得鐘健平一個<br />\n畀人圍點算"},{"pid":"2b30e8e01f810ef3d5528477d35941537f4598d3","tid":1366060,"uid":180960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r